# 🏗️ JEK Loyihasi — Chuqur Texnik Tahlil

## 📋 Umumiy Ma'lumot

| Xususiyat | Qiymat |
|---|---|
| **Framework** | NestJS v11 |
| **Til** | TypeScript v5.7 |
| **ORM** | Prisma v7 (PostgreSQL adapter) |
| **Ma'lumotlar bazasi** | PostgreSQL (pg + PrismaPg adapter) |
| **Autentifikatsiya** | JWT (Access + Refresh token) |
| **API hujjati** | Swagger (OpenAPI) |
| **Parol xashlash** | bcrypt (saltRounds: 12) |
| **Maqsad** | JEK (Jamoatchilik-kommunal xizmat) arizalar tizimi |

---

## 🗄️ Ma'lumotlar Bazasi Sxemasi (Prisma Schema)

### Modellar

```mermaid
erDiagram
    Users ||--o{ Requests : "yuboradi"
    Admins ||--o{ Requests : "assigned_jek"
    Requests ||--o{ RequestPhoto : "rasmlar"
    Requests ||--o{ RequestStatusLog : "status tarixi"

    Users {
        String id PK
        BigInt telegram_id
        String first_name
        String last_name
        String phoneNumber UK
        jekRoles role
        DateTime createdAt
        DateTime updatedAt
    }

    Admins {
        String id PK
        String first_name
        String last_name
        String phoneNumber UK
        String password
        District address
        jekRoles role
        Boolean isActive
        String jti
        String refreshToken
    }

    Requests {
        String id PK
        String request_number UK
        String user_id FK
        String address UK
        String assigned_jek_id FK
        Decimal latitude
        Decimal longitude
        String description
        Status_Flow status
        String rejection_reason
        DateTime completedAt
    }

    RequestPhoto {
        String id PK
        String request_id FK
        String file_url
        String telegram_file_id
        Int file_size
    }

    RequestStatusLog {
        String id PK
        String request_id FK
        Status_Flow old_status
        Status_Flow new_status
        String changed_by_role
        String changed_by_id
        String note
    }
```

### Enumlar

| Enum | Qiymatlar |
|---|---|
| `jekRoles` | [User](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/JEK/src/modules/users/users.service.ts#5-12), `JEK`, `GOVERNMENT`, `INSPECTION` |
| `District` | 12 ta Sirdaryo viloyati tumani/shahri |
| `Status_Flow` | `PENDING` → `ASSIGNED` → `IN_PROGRESS` → `COMPLETED` / `REJECTED` |

