## 🏛️ Arxitektura

```
src/
├── main.ts                         # Bootstrap, Swagger, ValidationPipe
├── app.module.ts                   # Root modul
├── common/
│   ├── decorators/
│   │   └── role.ts                 # @Roles() decorator
│   └── guards/
│       ├── token.guard.ts          # JWT tekshiruvi
│       └── role.guard.ts           # Rol tekshiruvi
├── core/
│   └── database/
│       ├── prisma.service.ts       # PrismaClient singleton
│       └── prsima.module.ts        # Global @Module (typo!)
└── modules/
    ├── auth/                       # Register/Login (faqat Admins)
    ├── admins/                     # Admin profil, status, parol
    └── users/                      # Foydalanuvchi ro'yxatdan o'tish (bo'sh!)
```

---

## 🔐 Autentifikatsiya va Xavfsizlik

### Token Guard ([token.guard.ts](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/JEK/src/common/guards/token.guard.ts))
- `Authorization: Bearer <token>` yoki `?token=<token>` dan qabul qiladi
- `JWT_ACCESS_SECRET` bilan tekshiradi
- Rol bo'yicha ([User](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/JEK/src/modules/users/users.service.ts#5-12) vs Admin) turli jadvaldan foydalanuvchi topadi
- Admin uchun **JTI (JWT ID) tekshiruvi** bor — eski sessiyani bloklash uchun

### Role Guard ([role.guard.ts](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/JEK/src/common/guards/role.guard.ts))
- `@Roles()` dekoratori bilan ishlaydi
- Admin bo'lsa `isActive === false` bo'lsa, blok qiladi
- Rolga mos kelmasa `ForbiddenException` chiqaradi

### Parol xavfsizligi
- bcrypt, `saltRounds: 12` — yaxshi
- Refresh token ham xashlangan holda saqlanadi

---

## 📦 Modullar Tahlili

### Auth Module
| Endpoint | Metod | Tavsif |
|---|---|---|
| `/auth/jek/register` | POST | Admin ro'yxatdan o'tish |
| `/auth/jel/login` | POST | Admin login |

> [!WARNING]
> **Typo!** `/auth/jel/login` — `jel` emas, `jek` bo'lishi kerak edi.

### Admins Module
| Endpoint | Metod | Guard | Tavsif |
|---|---|---|---|
| `/admins/self/data` | GET | TokenGuard + RoleGuard(JEK) | O'z profilini ko'rish |
| `/admins/update/status/:id` | PATCH | TokenGuard + RoleGuard(JEK) | Status o'zgartirish |
| `/admins/update/profile` | PATCH | TokenGuard + RoleGuard(JEK) | Profilni yangilash |
| `/admins/change/password` | PATCH | TokenGuard + RoleGuard(JEK) | Parol o'zgartirish |

### Users Module
| Endpoint | Metod | Guard | Tavsif |
|---|---|---|---|
| `/users` | POST | Yo'q | Foydalanuvchi ro'yxatdan o'tish |

> [!CAUTION]
> `UsersService.userRegister()` metodi **bo'sh** — hech narsa qaytarmaydi va hech nima saqlamaydi!

---

## 🐛 Topilgan Muammolar (Bugs & Issues)

### 1. 🔴 KRITIK — `userRegister()` bo'sh metod
**Fayl:** `src/modules/users/users.service.ts`
```ts
// Hozir:
userRegister(createUserDto: CreateUserDto) {
    // Bo'sh! Hech narsa qilmaydi!
}
```
Foydalanuvchi ro'yxatdan o'tishi **umuman ishlamaydi**.

---

### 2. 🔴 KRITIK — `CreateUserDto`da noto'g'ri import
**Fayl:** `src/modules/users/dto/create-user.dto.ts`
```ts
import { UserRole } from '@prisma/client'; // ❌ Bu mavjud emas!
// To'g'risi:
import { jekRoles } from '@prisma/client'; // ✅
```
Schema'da `UserRole` yo'q, faqat `jekRoles` bor. Bu **kompilatsiya xatosi** keltirib chiqaradi.

---

### 3. 🟡 MUHIM — URL Typo
**Fayl:** `src/modules/auth/auth.controller.ts:21`
```ts
@Post('jel/login') // ❌ "jel" noto'g'ri
@Post('jek/login') // ✅ "jek" bo'lishi kerak
```

---

### 4. 🟡 MUHIM — `Prisma schema`da `datasource` URL yo'q
```prisma
datasource db {
  provider = "postgresql"
  // url = env("DATABASE_URL")  ← YO'Q!
}
```
`url` maydoni **ko'rsatilmagan**. `PrismaService` `process.env.DATABASE_URL`dan o'zi oladi, lekin Prisma migration va generate uchun schema'da ham bo'lishi **shart**.

---

### 5. 🟡 MUHIM — `UpdateAdminDto`da ikki xil maydon konflikti
```ts
district?: District;  // ❌ Schema'da "district" maydoni yo'q
address?: District;   // ✅ Schema'da "address" bor
```
`district` maydoni ortiqcha va `updateAdminDto` to'g'ridan-to'g'ri Prisma update'ga berilganda xato chiqaradi.

---

### 6. 🟡 MUHIM — `isActive` logikasi noto'g'ri
**Fayl:** `src/modules/admins/admins.service.ts:69`
```ts
if (existJek.isActive && updateStatus.isActive) {
    throw new BadRequestException('Already active');
}
// Agar isActive false->false holati ham tekshirilmaydi!
```
Faqat `true->true` holat tekshirilgan. `false->false` (allaqachon o'chirilgan) holat ham tekshirilishi kerak.

---

### 7. 🟠 O'RTA — `remove()` metodi ishlanmagan
**Fayl:** `src/modules/admins/admins.service.ts:103`
```ts
remove(id: number) {
    return `This action removes a #${id} admin`; // Placeholder!
}
```
Bu controller'ga ulangan emas, lekin metod stub holida qoldirilgan.

---

### 8. 🟠 O'RTA — Token ichida juda ko'p ma'lumot
**Fayl:** `src/modules/auth/auth.service.ts:89`
```ts
const accessToken = await this.jwt.signAsync(existJek, { ... });
// existJek = butun Admins objekti (password hash bilan!)
```
JWT payload'ga butun `existJek` ob'ekti (refreshToken hash, password hash kabilar) kiritiladi. Faqat `{id, role, jti}` yetarli.

---

### 9. 🟢 KICHIK — Fayl nomi xatosi
**Fayl:** `src/core/database/prsima.module.ts` → `prisma.module.ts` bo'lishi kerak edi

---

### 10. 🟢 KICHIK — `jti` requestlar orasida hech qachon yangilanmaydi
Schema'da `jti String` bor lekin register/login methodlarda `jti` qiymati token'ga ham, bazaga ham **saqlanmayapti**. Token guard `user.jti !== payload.jti` tekshiradi — bu hamisha muvaffaqiyatsiz bo'ladi!

---

## ✅ Yaxshi Tomonlar

| Jihat | Baho |
|---|---|
| NestJS modular arxitekturasi | ✅ To'g'ri tuzilgan |
| Swagger integratsiyasi | ✅ `persistAuthorization` bilan |
| bcrypt saltRounds: 12 | ✅ Xavfsiz |
| `ValidationPipe` global | ✅ `whitelist: true` bilan |
| Refresh token xashlangan | ✅ Xavfsiz saqlash |
| `PrismaModule` global `@Global()` | ✅ Qayta import kerak emas |
| `OnModuleInit/Destroy` lifecycle | ✅ To'g'ri |
| `select` bilan faqat kerakli maydonlar | ✅ |
| O'zbek tilidagi xato xabarlari | ✅ Foydalanuvchiga qulay |

---

## 🚀 Tavsiyalar (Priority bo'yicha)

### 🔴 Darhol hal qilinishi kerak
1. `userRegister()` metodini to'ldiring
2. `CreateUserDto`dagi `UserRole` importini tuzating → `jekRoles`
3. `jti` ni login/register vaqtida generate qilib DB'ga saqlang
4. Schema'ga `url = env("DATABASE_URL")` qo'shing

### 🟡 Tez orada
5. Login URL typosini tuzating (`jel` → `jek`)
6. JWT token payload'dan `password`, `refreshToken` olib tashlang
7. `UpdateAdminDto`dan `district` maydonini olib tashlang
8. `updateStatus` metodida `false→false` tekshiruvini qo'shing

### 🟠 Keyinroq
9. Requests moduli yarating (hali yo'q!)
10. `GOVERNMENT` va `INSPECTION` rollar uchun endpointlar yarating
11. Fayl nomini `prsima.module.ts` → `prisma.module.ts` qilib rename qiling
12. Exception filtri qo'shing (global error handling)
13. Rate limiting qo'shing (brute-force himoyasi)

### 🟢 Kelajakda
14. Unit va integration testlar yozing
15. `.env` uchun `joi` yoki `zod` validation qo'shing
16. `helmet`, `cors` middleware qo'shing

---

